REPORT z_hello_world_formatted.

* This program shows variations of the basic Hello World example
* It is based on the "Try it yourself" tasks from README

WRITE: 'Hello World from ABAP!'.

* 1. Print your name
WRITE / 'Hello from', 'John Doe'.  " Change to your name

* 2. Add spacing
SKIP 2.

* 3. Add a separator line
ULINE.

* 4. Display multiple lines
WRITE / 'First line'.
WRITE / 'Second line'.
WRITE / 'Third line'.
